OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,FWith more than 80 artists showcasing
OL,7,Ftheir work, it gives people the rare
OL,8,Fopportunity to buy artwork directly
OL,9,Ffrom the makers themselves.
OL,11,FThe Borders Art Fair is held in Kelso
OL,12,Fevery March and has become the biggest
OL,13,Fevent of its kind in the region.
OL,15,FIt welcomes artists from the local
OL,16,Farea, and all over the UK, and
OL,17,Fexhibits everything from paintings, to
OL,18,Fsculptures, and ceramics.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
