PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,FThere are also interactive sessions
OL,7,Fwhere people can take part in art
OL,8,Fworkshops as well as watch live
OL,9,Fdemonstrations.
OL,11,FDirector Frances Fergusson says it's
OL,12,Fimportant that the event has something
OL,13,Ffor everyone.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,F"We have to make sure there's a real
OL,7,Fvariety of styles, mediums, and price
OL,8,Fpoints as well because we want
OL,9,Feverybody to enjoy art, so we've got
OL,10,Fthings that are for sale in the
OL,11,F#20,000 sort of region, but equally
OL,12,Fyou can pick up a print for under #50,
OL,13,Fand even some original oil paintings
OL,14,Ffrom #100.
OL,16,FThe art fair is carefully curated and
OL,17,Fbecause so many artists apply to be
OL,18,Finvolved, the team have the
OL,19,Fpainstaking job of having to turn away
OL,20,Faround a third of the people that
OL,21,Fapply each year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
