FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,FLuke Batchelor, a stone carver based
OL,7,Fin Coldstream, has exhibited there for
OL,8,Fthe last three years.
OL,10,FHe says the fair is a great
OL,11,Fopportunity for the creative community
OL,12,Fand the public to mix.
OL,14,F"The opportunity for artists to meet
OL,15,Fthe public is amazing because I'm
OL,16,Fnormally hidden away in my workshop,
OL,17,Fworking away so it's just so nice
OL,18,Fgetting that feedback from people.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,F"And I think people are really
OL,7,Finterested to meet you too so I can
OL,8,Ftell stories about my work and explain
OL,9,Fhow I use local stone and how my work
OL,10,Fis hand-carved, and I love doing that."
OL,12,FThe three day event attracted around
OL,13,F4,000 visitors.
OL,15,FFrances added, "It's a really good way
OL,16,Ffor artists to connect and hear what
OL,17,Fpeople think about their work, and
OL,18,Fwe've built a really nice community of
OL,19,Fartists too.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
