OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773748973
OL,3,CThousands attend Borders Art Fair in
OL,4,CKelso
OL,6,F"A few months later, I'll maybe see
OL,7,Fthat a gallery is showing an artist
OL,8,Fand I think that's just fantastic that
OL,9,Fthey met here."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
